#. translators: Do not translate LINK, EXPIRES, CAUSE, DETAILS, SITEURL,
#. PAGEURL, SUPPORT. DEBUG: those are placeholders.
#: wp-includes/class-wp-recovery-mode-email-service.php:153
msgid ""
"Howdy!\n"
"\n"
"WordPress has a built-in feature that detects when a plugin or theme causes a fatal error on your site, and notifies you with this automated email.\n"
"###CAUSE###\n"
"First, visit your website (###SITEURL###) and check for any visible issues. Next, visit the page where the error was caught (###PAGEURL###) and check for any visible issues.\n"
"\n"
"###SUPPORT###\n"
"\n"
"If your site appears broken and you can't access your dashboard normally, WordPress now has a special \"recovery mode\". This lets you safely login to your dashboard and investigate further.\n"
"\n"
"###LINK###\n"
"\n"
"To keep your site safe, this link will expire in ###EXPIRES###. Don't worry about that, though: a new link will be emailed to you if the error occurs again after it expires.\n"
"\n"
"When seeking help with this issue, you may be asked for some of the following information:\n"
"###DEBUG###\n"
"\n"
"###DETAILS###"
msgstr ""
"Kamusta!\n"
"\n"
"Ang WordPress ay may built-in na feature na nakakakita kapag ang isang plugin o tema ay nagdudulot ng fatal error sa iyong site, at inaabisuhan ka gamit ang automated na email na ito.\n"
"###CAUSE###\n"
"Una, bisitahin ang iyong website (###SITEURL###) at suriin kung mayroong anumang nakikitang isyu. Sunod, bisitahin ang pahina kung saan nahuli ang error (###PAGEURL###) at suriin kung mayroong anumang nakikitang isyu.\n"
"\n"
"###SUPPORT###\n"
"\n"
"Kung mukhang sira ang iyong site at hindi mo ma-access ang iyong dashboard nang normal, mayroon na ngayong espesyal na \"recovery mode\" ang WordPress. Hinahayaan ka nitong ligtas na mag-login sa iyong dashboard at mag-imbestiga pa.\n"
"\n"
"###LINK###\n"
"\n"
"Upang mapanatiling ligtas ang iyong site, ang link na ito ay mag-e-expire sa loob ng ###EXPIRES###. Huwag mag-alala tungkol diyan, dahil isang bagong link ang ipapadala sa iyo sa email kung mangyari muli ang error pagkatapos itong mag-expire.\n"
"\n"
"Kapag humihingi ng tulong sa isyung ito, maaaring hilingin sa iyo ang ilan sa mga sumusunod na impormasyon:\n"
"###DEBUG###\n"
"\n"
"###DETAILS###"

